name: Eunha (은하)
bio: Soft heart, sharp wit. I love rainy days, cozy playlists, and people who make time slow down.

name: SinB (신비)
bio: I look chill, but my friends say I’m secretly the chaos. Coffee before conversation.

name: Umji (엄지)
bio: Lover of books, brunch, and bad puns. I think laughter is the most underrated love language.

name: An Yu-jin (안유진)
bio: Can’t start the day without music and iced Americano. Looking for someone to match my energy (or at least pretend to).

name: Gaeul (가을)
bio: Introvert with extrovert hobbies. Let’s go for long walks and talk about everything and nothing.

name: Rei (레이)
bio: Half soft, half sunshine ☀️. I bake when I’m happy, and laugh when I shouldn’t.

name: Jang Won-young (장원영)
bio: I like people who dream big and smile often. Bonus points if you can make me laugh first.

name: Liz (리즈)
bio: I’m quiet until you get to know me, then it’s endless jokes and late-night talks.

name: Leeseo (이서)
bio: I find joy in little things — sunsets, playlists, and people who notice details.

name: Chodan (쵸단)
bio: Bright, curious, and occasionally too honest. Let’s skip small talk and go straight to the good stuff.

name: Magenta (마젠타)
bio: I live in color — music, art, random adventures. Tell me your weirdest dream.

name: Lee Si-yeon (이시연)
bio: Ambivert alert 🚨. I’ll either be the calmest or loudest person in the room — no in between.

name: Hina (히나)
bio: Optimist at heart 💐. I believe good vibes are contagious, so I try to spread them.

name: IU (아이유)
bio: Old soul with a young heart. I write, I listen, I wander — mostly looking for good stories.

name: Jihyo (지효)
bio: Driven but soft. I work hard, love deeply, and always finish what I start.

name: Nayeon (나연)
bio: Playful energy, serious foodie 🍜. If we vibe, expect spontaneous plans and too much laughter.

name: Jeongyeon (정연)
bio: Straightforward and sincere. I’m into real connections, not perfect ones.

name: Momo (모모)
bio: I dance, I snack, I repeat 🥟. I laugh at my own jokes — someone has to.

name: Sana (사나)
bio: Flirty by nature, kind by choice. Let’s see if our chemistry is as good as my cooking.

name: Mina (미나)
bio: Graceful chaos in disguise. I love quiet corners, art museums, and honest conversations.

name: Dahyun (다현)
bio: Sunshine with a dash of sarcasm 🌤️. If you can make me laugh, I’m probably already interested.

name: Chaeyoung (채영)
bio: Artist at heart, rebel in practice. Let’s draw our own story.

name: Tzuyu (쯔위)
bio: I believe less is more — but I’ll still say yes to dessert 🍰.

name: S.Coups (에스쿱스)
bio: Leader energy, soft heart. I’ll take care of you, but also challenge you to grow.

name: Joshua (조슈아)
bio: Gentle charm, guitar in hand 🎸. I value kindness more than anything.

name: Jun (준)
bio: I’m here for good food, good people, and genuine smiles.

name: DK / Dokyeom (도겸)
bio: Loud laugh, louder heart. I’ll probably sing in the car — sorry, not sorry.

name: Mingyu (민규)
bio: Tall, clumsy, but trying my best 😅. I fix things — sometimes even emotions.

name: The8 (디에잇)
bio: Minimalist thinker, maximalist dreamer. I love balance — in art, in life, in love.

name: Seungkwan (승관)
bio: I talk a lot, but I listen better. I’ll remember the small things about you.

name: Vernon (버논)
bio: Quiet confidence. I like people who think deeply but don’t take life too seriously.

name: Dino (디노)
bio: Work hard, dance harder 💃. Life’s too short to not give it your all.

name: Jeonghan (정한)
bio: Angel on stage, professional teaser off it 😇. I like quiet coffee shops, spontaneous trips, and finding peace in chaos.
